entry.title: Welcoming the fall semester!
entry.content: We are excited to welcome Elizabeth Haas, MPH, first year Epidemiology PhD student, to the Butler Population Sciences Research Group! Welcome, Elizabeth! In addition, we have had many exciting developments in our lab. We are looking forward to a great academic year!
